'''Anomalocaris''' is an {{Rarity|Uncommon}} fish found in the [[Ancient Isle]].

== Description ==
{{Description|The Anomalocaris is a large predator of the Ancient Isle. They flex their fins in a wave-like motion to generate speed, which they use to pursue prey. They bear strong armor-like scales on their backs, making them quite strong. The Anomalocaris went extinct around 485 million years ago at the end of the Ordovician period.|Bestiary Entry}}

